title: Logo for high-end early childhood education program. Targeting US pre-K moms.
description:
We sell a book + course for moms to help them prepare their 2 to 5-year-old children for kindergarten (and life) by following the best practices for early childhood education. The program is EXPENSIVE and is prepared by seasoned educators and curriculum designers - it is a high-value, personal approach program that includes coaching as well as self-paced materials.
The target audience is (non-teacher) moms who want to prepare their children for the academic journey in the best possible way. These moms buy parenting books already and want to be actively involved in raising their children. They do not put all the responsibility for the public school system/preschool to educate and raise their children.
However, since these moms are not teachers by education, they are still not 100% sure if their thoughts and methods are the right way. That's what our product gives - a certainty and structure for them to feel confident giving their child the best possible head start.
other_notes:
UPDATE about the logo design!:
Text "Kindergarten Prep" or "KINDERGARTEN PREP" needs to be in the focus, not the image itself. Ideally, this text will be displayed in a clever way - may be blended together with the design. Or if not, then the image/shape/geometry should be in front of the text, not on top of it.
The design needs to be WOW - something so different from anything else out there. It needs to stick out from the "crowd of brands" and penetrate mom's conscious and unconscious brain.
It needs to leave an impression. It has to be bold, and STAND for "best possible early childhood and parenting techniques and structure".
We want the logo to be memorable, and be on mom's minds whenever they think about kindergarten prep and early childhood education.

title: Purpose Front: We Deliver Purpose Products
description: We are Purpose Front, an e-commerce marketplace startup that partners with purposeful people (organizations and individuals) to design, market, and sell products that supporters and potential supporters actually want to buy. Our platform amplifies the voices of these purpose-driven people while elevating their funding.
other_color_requirements: We're playing around with Pantone 17-3834 TCX (#7E6EAC). Please reference image with color palate.
other_notes:
Our designs need to communicate purpose while recognizing that the way we support it is through the sale of high quality products: this is a difficult design problem. How do you balance sales reality and purpose priority?
We will be running marketing campaigns for the product lines we create for purposeful people we have contracts with. So we need a logo that allows us to accentuate their purpose, products, and brand while still piquing interest in Purpose Front itself. Like Stripe, we'd rather service other brands than be recognized by the consumer primarily.
After a quick brainstorm, we decided that the following concepts were worth exploring:
- Our brand is a storefront that elevates, displays, and communicates purpose.
- Our brand hides behind the purposes we support, letting them take center stage.
- Our brand is light and airy in order to support that cause.
- Our brand should be able to be expressed iconographically for minimal branding but should also have a lettering component for home page and certain marketing materials.
- Feel free to play around with the slogan, "Products from Purpose", but the main asset likely won't feature it.
Please ask any questions by shooting me an email at isaiah@purposefront.com!

title: Logo for portal about Solar Power
description:
SOLARINFO is the leading Spanish B2B portal about Solar Power with daily news, articles, etc.
It is targeted towards professionals (installers, designers, energy managers, etc.) that work within the fields of Solar Energy.
Solar energy is radiant light and heat from the Sun that is harnessed using a range of technologies such as solar power to generate electricity. The portal SOLARINFO cover the use of photovoltaic systems, concentrated solar power, and solar water heating to harness the energy.
SOLARINFO forms part of Grupo Tecma Red (www.grupotecmared.es ) which is Spain's leading Editorial Company specialized in providing information and knowledge about Sustainability, Energy, and New Technologies for Buildings and Cities.
other_notes:
NAME:
- SOLARINFO
USE:
- The logo will be used as a header on our daily news portal about Solar Energy.
- Solar Energy is a technology that is based upon capturing solar light on panels and transform it to energy. This should be reflected in the logo!
- The logos should have the same "structure" and "proportions" as our other portals:
- ESMARTCTIY: http://www.esmartcity.es (smart cities)
- CONSTRUIBLE: http://www.construible.es (sustainable building)
- ESEFICIENCIA: http://www.eseficiencia.es (energy efficiency)
- CASADOMO: http://www.casadomo.com (intelligent buildings)
- SMARTGRIDSINFO: http://www.smartgridsinfo.es (smart grids)
TEXT:
- The design should be a horizontal 2 line design:
- First Line: SOLARINFO.es (it might also be written SOLARinfo.es) with the .es written vertically
- Second Line: Todo Sobre Energía Solar
- The word SOLARINFO should be dominating
- The background of the logo should be white (transparent)
- Some kind of graphical image (such as a sun and solar panel) should be included, although it should be totally integrated within the text (not as a separate image).
STYLE:
- We prefer a Flat, Simple and Modern design.
COLOUR INFO:
- The main colour for the log and especially the word SOLAR should be dark yellow (the same yellow will be used as the theme colour on the portal for some lines, backgrounds, fonts, etc.)
- Also other colours could also be used, for example, gray for the word INFO/info
- The text on the second line: "Todo Sobre Energía Solar" should be in dark gray
DELIVERABLES:
- Background:
- All files should be on transparent background.
- Vector Design
- Original in Vector Design.
- Size and Resolution:
- The originals shall be 300 dpi and 30 cm wide (aprox. 12 inches).
- The canvas size should not be much bigger than the logo, just slightly separated from the border of the logo, with the same space both vertically and horizontally.
- Colour Versions:
- 4 colour versions: colour, grayscale, all black, all white.
- File formats
- 6 file formats: AI (editable original), EPS, SVG, PNG, JPG, PDF (vector)
- File Names:
- solarinfo-logo-colour
- solarinfo-logo-gray
- solarinfo-logo-black
- solarinfo-logo-white
- Favicon:
- A favicon.ico 16x16 + 32x32 pixel with transparent background should be included (using full width with no empty space around). The favicon should use a representable part of the logo (letter, etc.).
- Proofsheet:
- A Proofsheet (indicating colours, fonts, etc.) should be delivered.

Realizzo contenuti video personali e professionali.
il nome della mia attività professionale è Emanuele Coco Videoproduzioni.
Il nome dell'etichetta invece con cui produco video personali è Kok'n'Roll.
Stò realizzando una piattaforma streaming in stile Netflix dove pubblicherò i miei lavori personali e mi serve un logo pensato che rappresenti una casa di produzione video.
Il logo che ho attualmente è amatoriale e non va bene.
Vorrei avere un logo che da l’idea di una casa di produzione cinematografica, una azienda che realizza film
other_notes:
Non cerco solo la scritta, ma anche un marchio associato ad essa, o comunque in alternativa una scritta che contenga anche grafica
possiedo già un logo kok'n'roll ma non è assolutamente attuale e professionale.
Accetto qualsiasi idea ma ho bisogno di un logo che mi possa essere utile sia nel privato che nel professionale.
il miei lavori li trovate qua http://www.emanuelecoco.it mentre i miei filmati personali sono qua: https://www.youtube.com/user/koknroll
Vorrei avere un logo che da l’idea di una casa di produzione cinematografica, una azienda che realizza film

title: Logo for an investment fund contributing to the fight against climate change
description:
We are an environmental investment fund focused on climate change and decarbonizing the planet. We are contributing to our collective fight against climate change and helping preserve the planet for future generations.
We are focused on raising money from large, sophisticated institutional investors (endowments, foundations, pension funds, wealthy families, wealthy individuals) around the world -- U.S., Europe, and Asia.
other_notes:
Klima is the German word for climate.
Starting ideas would be a stylized tree, leaf, globe, or letter K.
We are open to a color background but also want a version that has a transparent background so it is versatile for website, printing, etc.

title: Design a bright and creative logo for Paradise at the Beach!!
slogan_to_incorporate: An Ocean Breeze Puts the Mind at Ease
description: I have a vacation rental business at the beach in North Myrtle Beach, SC. We host all different groups but, our target demographics are families.
other_notes: I am interested in the designers using their imaginations. I do not want to stifle creativity. I would love something fun and relaxing with a Palmetto tree and something beachy and relaxing. However, I am open to anything! I would prefer it not to be an emblem layout. I love the font in the attached logo

title: A.S. Ford Properties LLC Logo design
description: Buy and sell distressed properties and try to help the owners find solutions to their financial problems
other_color_requirements: I have very little input on color. I would just prefer the overall look be professional, but not too corporate. And have an upbeat look, comforting look
other_notes:
I want something professional looking, but not too stuffy. I'd like the design to be warm and comforting as opposed to cold and distant. We deal with people who are in difficult financial situations and I want the image to be comforting and inviting but also professional.
I think the design should incorporate a font, a house, maybe a nice landscape, the sun. An overall cheery design. It could be abstract let your imagination take you where it will!

title: Design our new Physical Therapy Company Logo
description:
We provide Physical Therapy to patients of all age ranges.
We promote fitness and wellness.
We pride ourselves with our knowledge, industry experience, patient satisfaction, and integrity.
Location - We have currently have clinics in OH, FL, TX, and MD, but looking to expand to other states.
other_notes: We would really like to highlight a road/street design in our logo. We want to focus our patients on their "path or road" to recovery. A person icon on the road is good as well. Open to all ideas.

description: StarCard Sports Games (SCS) is a mobile based play-to-earn blockchain game.
other_notes: This is just an idea, but a bright star shining down into some sort of a stadium could look really great. This is just an idea though, and I am open to all ideas! UPDATE: So far, we have only received images of stadiums. That is great, but we are open to ALL IDEAS. Thank you so much!
